public class GetAirportsInRectangleTask
extends QueryTask<GetAirportsInRectangleTask.QueryParams,Collection<Airport>>

Background task to get airports in a rectangle (which is a fairly slow query). Clients should call AsyncTask.execute(Params...) to start the background task.
